    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.51 * v2 + 0.20)) - (0.49 + wp.abs(v2 + 0.79)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.64) - (v1 + 0.13 * tmp + 0.56)) + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.58) / wp.exp(tmp + 0.45)))
    v2 = 0.91
    tmp = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.87 - v2 + 0.38) * 0.07))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin(v2))
